name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForMitochondrialDisorders
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Mitochondrial Disorders
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to mitochondrial disorders and is listed as a neurologic disorder on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes mitochondrial disorders. It includes Friedreich's ataxia, cytochrome c oxidase deficiency, and pyruvate carboxylase deficiency.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
